original_title: Betty & Veronica: An Archie Comics XXX Parody
overview: 'Betty and Veronica share everything - except Archie Andrews. When Veronica's study session with Archie is interrupted by a broken sink, Betty shows up JUST in time to interrupt. Will Betty and Veronica FINALLY learn to share?"
